29
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:12,260
作为母亲  它要尽其所能发挥本领
It will take all her strength and skill as a mother

30
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:15,170
保护并养育幼崽
to protect and provide for them,

31
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:18,330
才能将它们抚养到成年
if she is to raise them to adulthood.

