00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:38,940
这片森林有老虎家庭生活所需的一切
This forest has everything a tiger family needs.

34
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:43,950
充足的淡水
Plenty of fresh water,

35
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:55,740
可供藏身的密集灌木
dense thickets for concealment,

36
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:03,120
还有遍布猎物的开阔草原
and open grasslands full of prey.

37
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:28,030
在巢穴中与幼崽挨过饥肠辘辘的两周之后
After two hungry weeks confined to the den with her cubs,

