迁至新巢后全家安全
The family are safe at a new den.

54
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:11,450
像拉吉贝拉这样经验丰富的母虎
An experienced tigress like Raj Bera

55
00:09:11,450 --> 00:09:14,590
可能知道数个像这样的藏匿处
may know half a dozen hideaways like this.

56
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:28,850
尽管它捕猎失败
Even though she failed in her hunt,

57
00:09:28,850 --> 00:09:32,160
幼崽依然渴望它的乳汁
the cubs are as hungry for milk as ever.

58
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:48,400
养育并保护多达四只幼崽
For a tigress to feed and protect,

59
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:52,640
对于母虎来说是严峻的挑战
as many as four young is a relentless challenge.

60
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:07,620
它不太可能将所有幼崽都养大
It's unlikely that she will be able to raise them all.

61
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,920
而如今在印度
And in India today,

62
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:28,080
新的压力使抚养幼崽至成年
there are new pressures, making it harder than ever

63
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,600
变得前所未有的艰难
to rear a family to adulthood.

64
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:38,400
拉吉贝拉的领地面积刚好够它养育幼崽
Raj Bera's territory is just big enough to support her cubs,

65
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:38,580
拉吉贝拉

