00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:43,130
但它被其它老虎的领地包围
but she's surrounded by territories held by other tigers.

67
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:48,020
而整个保护区被人类居住区环绕
And all are encircled by human settlement.

68
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:49,440
班达迦老虎保护区

69
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:04,480
班达迦共有约八十只老虎
There are about 80 tigers in Bandhavgarh.

70
00:11:07,020 --> 00:11:10,180
密度高得非比寻常
This is an unusually high density.

71
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:24,940
对于生存空间的竞争十分激烈
Competition for space is intense.

72
00:11:34,890 --> 00:11:39,380
脸上的伤疤是对手间争斗的证明
Scarred faces are evidence of battles between rivals.

73
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,480
为了保证领地安全
To keep her territory secure,

74
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:53,020
拉吉贝拉定期在长达十九千米的边界巡逻
Raj Bera regularly patrols its 12-mile-long boundary.

75
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:06,080
它每次喷尿  都是在标记
Each time she sprays, she's marking a line

76
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:09,360
其它老虎不得逾越的界线
that other tigers know they cross at their peril.

77
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:19,460
耐着正午的酷热标记领地十分辛苦
Territory marking in the midday heat is hard work.

78
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:45,800
它需要降温
She needs to cool off.

79
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:11,050
一只多情的雄孔雀
An amorous male peacock.

80
00:14:39,010 --> 00:14:40,170
每一天
Every day,

81
00:14:40,170 --> 00:14:44,190
它都在三项任务间取得近乎不可能的平衡
she has to strike an almost impossible balance,

82
00:14:45,970 --> 00:14:48,970
分配时间进行捕猎
dividing her time between hunting,

83
00:14:49,290 --> 00:14:51,520
对领地边界进行气味标记
scent marking her boundaries,

84
00:14:52,610 --> 00:14:54,710
以及照料幼崽
and nursing her cubs.

85
00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:07,500
目前  幼崽的需求必须优先满足
For now the demands of her young family must take precedence.

86
00:15:19,690 --> 00:15:23,730
它的幼崽已成长到开始探索的阶段
Her cubs have reached the stage when they start exploring.

87
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:34,570
尽管它们仍未完全学会走路
Although even walking hasn't been completely mastered.

88
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:45,310
幼崽之间的差异逐渐显现
Differences between the cubs are beginning to appear.

89
00:15:47,690 --> 00:15:51,240
三个兄弟忙着打闹
The three brothers are caught up in a rough and tumble.

90
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:57,310
但它们的姐妹比芭  踌躇退缩
But their sister, Biba, holds back.

91
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:11,690
它体型较小  也不如它的兄弟强壮
She is smaller and not as strong as her brothers.

92
00:16:12,890 --> 00:16:16,620
这些差异只会随着它们的成长
And these differences will only become more apparent,

93
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:18,370
变得愈发明显
as they grow older.

94
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:50,280
两个月后
Two months later

95
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:54,380
老虎一家永远地离开了巢穴
and the family has left the den for good.

96
00:16:57,220 --> 00:17:00,850
幼崽现已足够强壮  能跟上母亲
The cubs are now strong enough to follow their mother.

97
00:17:12,370 --> 00:17:15,790
母虎必须开始教育幼崽了
She must now start on their education.

98
00:17:17,850 --> 00:17:20,250
它带它们巡视领地
She shows them around her territory.

99
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:26,130
更重要的是  带它们品尝一种新食物
And most importantly, introduces them to a new diet.

100
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:30,020
肉
Meat.

101
00:17:34,850 --> 00:17:37,040
幼崽的体型长大了一倍
The cubs have doubled in size,

102
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:39,710
所以它必须更频繁地狩猎
so that she has to hunt even more frequently

103
00:17:39,710 --> 00:17:42,470
来满足它们日益增长的胃口
to provide for their growing appetites.

104
00:18:06,850 --> 00:18:08,820
自从它的幼崽出生
Since the birth of her cubs,

105
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:12,240
拉吉贝拉便无法像过去那样
Raj Bera has not been able to patrol her territory

106
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:14,490
定期巡逻领地
as regularly as she did.

107
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:22,030
这使对手有机可乘
And that has given a rival an opportunity.

108
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,900
这是索萝
This is Solo,

109
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:29,750
拉吉贝拉的成年女儿
Raj Bera's adult daughter.

110
00:18:33,910 --> 00:18:38,270
它擅自闯入了母亲的领土
And she is trespassing on her mother's lands,

111
00:18:39,050 --> 00:18:42,830
整个班达迦最富饶的地方之一
some of the richest in the whole of Bandhavgarh.

112
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:49,440
它或许不知道拉吉贝拉在这里狩猎
She may be unaware that Raj Bera is hunting here.

113
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:01,920
通常成年老虎会相互避开
Normally adult tigers avoid each other.

114
00:19:06,630 --> 00:19:11,400
因为即便是母女打斗也有可能致命
Because ﬁghts even between mother and daughter can be fatal.

115
00:19:18,610 --> 00:19:22,990
不过目前  索萝似乎是在试探它的母亲
But now, Solo appears to be testing her mother.

116
00:20:00,490 --> 00:20:03,540
面对拉吉贝拉稳操胜券的步伐
Faced with Raj Bera's confident advance,

117
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:05,610
索萝立刻表现出顺从
Solo immediately defers,

118
00:20:05,610 --> 00:20:08,100
像幼崽一样露出腹部
rolling on her back like a cub.

119
00:20:11,930 --> 00:20:14,690
它还不够成熟  不够强壮
She's not old enough or strong enough

120
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:16,920
难以争夺领土
