121
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:19,210
暂时不能
Yet.

122
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:28,410
拉吉贝拉仍然是这里的统治者
Raj Bera is still the ruler here.

123
00:20:33,550 --> 00:20:36,720
但是索萝发出了警告
But Solo has issued a warning.

124
00:20:54,100 --> 00:20:56,060
领土重归安全
With their territory secure,

125
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:59,830
全家得以一起放松
the family can relax together.

126
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:10,810
幼崽现在把越来越多的时间
The cubs are now spending more and more time

127
00:21:10,810 --> 00:21:14,210
用在锻炼协调性和灵活性上
developing their coordination and agility.

128
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:22,070
它们从游戏中学习
And they do that through play.

129
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:47,970
一头野猪
A wild boar.

130
00:21:56,030 --> 00:21:59,330
它可能是成年老虎菜单上的美味
It could be on the menu of an adult tiger.

131
00:22:04,380 --> 00:22:08,510
但其中一只幼年公虎有点急功近利
But one of the male cubs is being a little ambitious.

132
00:22:14,830 --> 00:22:16,600
还是等等吧
Perhaps not yet.

133
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:36,120
班达迦的冬季降临
Winter arrives in Bandhavgarh.

134
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:09,490
幼崽九个月大了
The cubs are nine months old.

135
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:15,350
步入了青春期
In their adolescence.

136
00:23:16,570 --> 00:23:20,620
邻居开始对它们更加提防
And the neighbours are beginning to take them more seriously.

137
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:40,840
目前拉吉贝拉顺利让它的幼崽都活了下来
Raj Bera has done well to keep all her cubs alive so far.

138
00:23:42,710 --> 00:23:45,810
一般只有百分之五十的幼崽
Typically only 50% of tiger cubs

139
00:23:45,810 --> 00:23:47,820
能幸存到成年
survive to adulthood.

140
00:23:54,620 --> 00:23:58,550
不过现在  家庭关系开始改变
But now, the family relationships are changing.

141
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:23,040
它不再让幼崽先吃
She no longer lets the cubs eat first.

142
00:24:25,500 --> 00:24:28,360
它必须让它们明白总有一天
She has to teach them that one day

143
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,980
它们需要自力更生
they will have to provide for themselves.

144
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:41,640
等它饱食餍足
Once she has had her fill,

145
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:44,540
它的儿子占据尸体
her sons dominate the carcass.

146
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:58,040
只有等它们吃完
It's only when they have finished

147
00:24:58,040 --> 00:24:59,930
体型较小的女儿  比芭
that their smaller sister, Biba,

148
00:24:59,930 --> 00:25:03,310
才能不受打扰地进食
gets her chance to feed undisturbed.

149
00:25:24,970 --> 00:25:28,380
警报提示有入侵者
Alarm calls warn of an intruder.

150
00:25:35,330 --> 00:25:39,000
这次是一只成年公虎
This time it's an adult male tiger.

151
00:25:41,360 --> 00:25:45,790
它的体型比拉吉贝拉大三分之一  更加强壮
He‘s a third bigger than Raj Bera and much more powerful.

152
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:56,120
这是幼崽最喜欢的水洼
This is the cubs' favourite water hole.

153
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:12,660
母亲和儿子
Mother and sons

