Adult male tigers sometimes kill cubs,

157
00:27:19,740 --> 00:27:22,930
所以接近一只公虎风险极高
so, to approach one is a huge risk.

158
00:27:27,450 --> 00:27:30,930
当然  除非它是你的父亲
Unless of course he's your father,

159
00:27:33,610 --> 00:27:37,380
森林里唯一不会伤害它的公虎
the only male in the forest who would never harm her.

160
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:46,360
公虎很少见到自己的后代
Tiger fathers rarely meet their offspring.

161
00:27:49,010 --> 00:27:52,250
它似乎也不想跟女儿熟络
And he doesn't seem keen to get acquainted.

162
00:27:57,870 --> 00:28:00,660
但是只要它在森林里巡逻
But while he is patrolling the forest,

163
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:02,700
其它公虎就会绕道而行
other males will keep away.

164
00:28:02,700 --> 00:28:05,020
幼崽就是安全的
And the cubs will be safe.

165
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:25,670
至于其它的一切  幼崽依赖拉吉贝拉照料
For everything else, the cubs depend on Raj Bera.

166
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:35,370
