She still has to provide for the whole family.

167
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,340
夏季到来
It's summer.

168
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:13,830
接下来的几周  灼热的高温
Over the next few weeks the searing heat

169
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:16,430
