171
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:47,150
班达迦必须承受十年来最严重的干旱
And Bandhavgarh has to endure the worst drought in a decade.

172
00:29:55,220 --> 00:29:58,670
这是秃鹫的好时机
It's a good time to be a vulture.

