00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:11,100
吸引着保护区干渴难耐的居民
become magnets for the park's thirsty inhabitants.

175
00:30:22,340 --> 00:30:25,200
通常  叶猴大部分时间
Normally, langurs spend most of their time

176
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:27,230
都在遥不可及的树上
out of reach in the trees.

177
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:32,260
但干旱期间
But during the drought,

178
00:30:32,280 --> 00:30:35,880
它们必须冒险穿过开阔地带去喝水
they must risk crossing open ground to get water.

179
00:30:57,910 --> 00:31:00,510
一旦勇敢的成年叶猴开始行动
Once the braver adults make their move,

180
00:31:00,510 --> 00:31:02,620
剩下的成员便紧随其后
the rest of the troop follow.

181
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:17,730
离开安乐窝  它们紧张不安
Out of their comfort zone, they're nervous.

182
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,300
这里没有危险
No danger here,

183
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,900
至少在它看来
as far as she can see.

184
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:04,000
但是你不可能在喝水的同时观望四周
But you can't drink and watch all at the same time.

185
00:32:50,770 --> 00:32:53,940
在拉吉贝拉的领土中心
Here in the heart of Raj Bera’s territory,

186
00:32:54,190 --> 00:32:58,080
这些水洼成了旱季期间
these water holes become the focus of the family's life

187
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:00,950
家庭生活的焦点
throughout these driest months.

188
00:33:18,180 --> 00:33:22,650
被吸引至水洼的不只有猎物
It's not just prey that are drawn here to the water holes.

189
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:28,060
新的入侵者
A new trespasser.

190
00:34:06,490 --> 00:34:11,900
看来这只母虎今天不打算宣告主权
It seems this tigress is weary of pressing her claim today.

191
00:34:13,580 --> 00:34:15,330
但是很显然现在有
But it's clear there are now

192
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:18,760
更多的对手觊觎拉吉贝拉的狩猎领地
more rivals for Raj Bera's hunting territory.

193
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:43,160
现在遥远的嚎叫预示着以后的麻烦
And now distant roars signal further trouble.

194
00:34:51,700 --> 00:34:54,600
索萝  拉吉贝拉的成年女儿
Solo, Raj Bera's adult daughter,

195
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:57,140
正在进行第一次交配
is mating for the first time.

196
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:29,650
很快它会产下需要喂养的幼崽
She will soon have her own family with new mouths to feed.

197
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:42,840
那时离它回来就不远了
And it‘s not long before she's back,

198
00:35:42,870 --> 00:35:45,650
在它母亲的领地深处狩猎
hunting deep in her mother's territory.

199
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,910
它在偷猎
She is poaching.

200
00:36:17,210 --> 00:36:21,240
一岁大的幼崽需要互相
The year-old cubs are practising their hunting skills

201
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:22,270
磨练捕猎技术
on each other.

202
00:36:26,650 --> 00:36:30,740
捕捉猎物需要力量和敏捷
Capturing prey requires power and agility.

203
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:41,220
同时还需伏击和攻击的能力
As well as the skills of ambush and attack.

204
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:53,540
为了生存它们需要掌握猎杀技巧
Their survival will depend on mastering the ability to kill.

205
00:37:01,570 --> 00:37:03,630
但在未来的八个月里
But for another eight months,

206
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:06,450
母亲依然要继续喂养它们
their mother must continue to provide.

207
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:10,810
她捕猎的工作量也大大增加
And she's having to work much harder now.

208
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:17,070
即使是这般大小的猎物
Even a kill as big as this

209
00:37:17,070 --> 00:37:20,320
也只够全家吃几天
won't last the family more than a couple of days.

210
00:37:22,470 --> 00:37:25,560
它的儿子们先进食
Her sons are the first to every meal

211
00:37:28,130 --> 00:37:30,590
并小心翼翼守护着自己那份食物
and jealously guard their share.

212
00:37:32,070 --> 00:37:34,800
比芭只能等待
Biba is forced to wait.

213
00:37:53,970 --> 00:37:57,620
倘若还剩零星碎肉就已经很幸运了
She will be lucky if she gets anything more than scraps.

214
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:25,100
离开它吃饱了的兄弟们
Leaving her well-fed brothers behind,

215
00:38:28,430 --> 00:38:31,520
比芭试图自己捕猎
Biba tries to hunt for herself.

216
00:38:38,260 --> 00:38:41,440
它已看过母亲多次示范
She's watched her mother do this many times.

217
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:47,280
跟踪猎物
Stalk,

218
00:38:50,080 --> 00:38:51,120
并俯身
and drop.

219
00:39:09,470 --> 00:39:13,320
它已经掌握了隐身技术
She has mastered the technique of becoming invisible.

220
00:39:17,550 --> 00:39:22,060
但它的体型和力量都还不足以发起突袭
But she doesn't yet have the size or strength to strike.

221
00:39:36,470 --> 00:39:40,640
强风预示着雨季的来临
Strong winds signal the arrival of the monsoon.

222
00:40:25,380 --> 00:40:27,680
对多数居住在森林里的动物来说
The abundance of water means that,

223
00:40:27,680 --> 00:40:30,030
充沛的水源意味着
for most of the forest's inhabitants,

224
00:40:30,030 --> 00:40:32,230
好时节又回来了
the good times have returned.

225
00:40:38,470 --> 00:40:43,280
但雨季对拉吉贝拉一家来说是最坏的季节
But the monsoon is the worst time for Raj Bera and her family.

226
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:48,930
它的猎物不再依赖于水洼
Her prey are no longer dependent on the water holes.

227
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:56,090
而是可以在它的领地里四散生活
They are now free to disperse throughout her territory.

228
00:41:03,110 --> 00:41:06,190
这使伏击变得难上加难
They will be much harder for her to ambush.

229
00:41:19,240 --> 00:41:23,190
几周后  在它领地的西界附近
A few weeks later near the western boundary of her lands,

230
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,590
发生了一场打斗
there has been a fight.

231
00:41:28,210 --> 00:41:30,720
拉吉贝拉不幸负伤
And Raj Bera is injured.

232
00:41:48,290 --> 00:41:50,760
母虎严重负伤
A serious injury to a mother tiger

233
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:53,670
意味着它的幼崽会挨饿
can mean starvation for her cubs.

234
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:24,730
比芭总是最后一个
Biba is invariably the last

235
00:42:24,730 --> 00:42:26,790
享用母亲狩猎成果的孩子
to benefit from her mother's hunting.

236
00:42:29,190 --> 00:42:31,440
它急需自力更生
She needs to fend for herself.

237
00:42:31,530 --> 00:42:34,620
为此它必须找到属于自己的领地
And to do that, she must find her own territory,

238
00:42:34,620 --> 00:42:36,430
远离它的兄弟
away from her brothers.

239
00:43:01,350 --> 00:43:03,450
但它能去哪呢
But where can she go?

240
00:43:09,590 --> 00:43:12,810
其他的领地早已被占领
Every other territory is already occupied.

241
00:43:17,900 --> 00:43:22,710
它只能被迫离开班达迦向外搜寻
She's forced to search outside Bandhavgarh altogether.

242
00:43:33,230 --> 00:43:36,250
它母亲也会与它永别
Her mother will never see her again.

243
00:43:51,110 --> 00:43:54,070
雄性幼崽也饥肠辘辘
The male cubs are also going hungry.

244
00:44:15,550 --> 00:44:19,370
它们也在试着自力更生
They, too, are trying to fend for themselves.

245
00:44:32,630 --> 00:44:35,810
对于新手来说  鹿太过警觉
The deer are too alert for novices.

246
00:44:50,420 --> 00:44:53,770
有三只嗷嗷待哺的青年雄性幼崽
With the demands of three adolescent male cubs

247
00:44:53,770 --> 00:44:56,690
再加上它对手日渐增长的敌意
and increasing hostility from her rivals,

248
00:44:56,920 --> 00:45:01,340
拉吉贝拉面临自己的王朝有史以来最大的威胁
Raj Bera is facing the greatest ever threat to her dynasty.

249
00:45:03,860 --> 00:45:06,210
它迈了一大步
She takes a drastic step

250
00:45:06,280 --> 00:45:10,700
离开安全的公园  希望找到更易捕猎之物
and leaves the safety of the park in the hope of easier prey.

251
00:45:16,390 --> 00:45:19,070
邻近村庄的牛
Cattle in the neighbouring villages.

252
00:45:30,510 --> 00:45:34,160
雌虎与人类之间一直存在冲突
For tigress and people, there is real danger here.

253
00:45:34,450 --> 00:45:38,130
而且拉吉贝拉无法战胜对方
It's a conflict that Raj Bera cannot win.

254
00:46:49,380 --> 00:46:51,480
次日黎明时分
Dawn, the next day.

255
00:47:14,490 --> 00:47:16,250
拉吉贝拉
Raj Bera.

256
00:47:32,990 --> 00:47:35,940
被公园工作人员解救
She was rescued by the park authorities

257
00:47:35,940 --> 00:47:38,580
并重新回到自己的领地
and released back into her territory,

258
00:47:38,580 --> 00:47:40,620
一家团聚
to rejoin her family.

259
00:48:04,070 --> 00:48:05,920
过去两年里
Over the last two years,

260
00:48:05,920 --> 00:48:09,490
它含辛茹苦养育自己的幼崽长大
she's struggled to raise her cubs safely to this point.

261
00:48:09,710 --> 00:48:11,840
尽管失去了女儿
And although she's lost her daughter,

262
00:48:11,850 --> 00:48:15,030
但它的儿子即将成年
her sons are on the brink of adulthood.

263
00:48:18,010 --> 00:48:19,560
排除万难
Against the odds,

264
00:48:19,580 --> 00:48:22,860
它仍有机会为自己的老虎王朝
she still has the chance to secure the future

265
00:48:22,860 --> 00:48:24,750
提供一个美好的未来
of her tiger dynasty.
